              </div>
              <h2 className="text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4">Cancel Order?</h2>
              <p className="text-slate-500 font-medium mb-12">Are you sure you want to cancel your order for {cancelConfirmOrder.productName}? Items will be returned to the farmer's stock.</p>
              <div className="space-y-4">
